title: Living With Expectancy | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Living With Expectancy | Joel Osteen
description:
God wants to do incredible things in your life, but you have to do your part and raise your level of expectancy. Start believing for more of God's favor. He is looking for ways to be good to you! 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
